## Development

```bash
pnpm test       # run tests
pnpm build      # compile TypeScript
pnpm start      # run compiled output
```

## Security note

This server uses the MCP Streamable HTTP transport. In production, place it behind a reverse proxy that handles:
- TLS termination
- Authentication (OAuth 2.1 + PKCE per the MCP spec)
- Rate limiting
